        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "The sect of the Pharisees; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " these Pharisees were a sect amongst the Jews, (so called from vrp ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "separavit, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and may be Englished, separatists), separating from converse with others, by reason of an opinion they had of their own holiness, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Luke 18:11",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Luke 18:11",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
